    <note>He(2) Dan [12732] His nephew was Chushun [12741] and Zhitong's [7033] great grandson was Chuhuo [12739]. Zhitong's grandson, Yue [12734], has the same generational name as Dan [12732] (water radical) and his son, Chuquan [12735] , has the same generational name as Zhitong's great grandsons and Dan's sons. Therefore, I am considering Dan a grandson of Zhitong and a nephew of Dian [12732] (Yue's father) and the other Longquan Chu+x generational minzi as also nephews of Dan. The exact relationships may be different, but addresses, generational names and chronological logic all suggest that the generational and lineage identifications are accurate. Zhejiang TZ, 125.31b. CBD, 2, 1280, 1265.From Hartwell's ACTIVITY table:1196:  Apt. Canzhi zhengshi (State Council).1200:  Apt. concurrently Zhi Shumi yuan shi.1201:  Replaced in both state counsil positions by Chen Ziqiang and dismissed.</note>
